# Local frontend config
#
# The frontend is served on your machine (yarn dev → http://localhost:3000).
# It calls the REMOTE preview backend API so you don't have to run one locally.
# Tokens are stored in localStorage on the localhost:3000 origin, and the
# Distil extension's content script syncs them into extension storage.
